data.description: OPEN 2/11 from 1-3pm. Discover the charm of this 3-bedroom, 2-story nestled in the Mayfair/Eastmoor neighborhood! Beautiful colonial layout w/ formal dining room perfect for hosting gatherings, & a cozy family room boasts a wood-burning fireplace, creating a warm & inviting atmosphere. Hardwood floors grace much of the home, including the upstairs. Natural sunlight streams in through ample windows (replaced 2022 w/ transferable warranty), brightening every corner. The unique hip roof design adds character & creates captivating arched ceilings in all bedrooms. Full basement for ample storage.  2 car detached garage w/ opener. The roof to house was replaced in 2019, & garage roof replaced 2023. New furnace 2022. New hot water tank 2021. Large backyard perfect for warm nights! Don't miss it!
